race.name: O'Reilly Auto Parts 500
race.comments: Kyle Busch won the O'Reilly Auto Parts 500 at Texas Motor Speedway, his 44th Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series victory. Prior to the start of the race, the following cars dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reasons indicated: #17 (backup car), #24 (engine change), #32 (transmissioon change) and #42 (failing pre-race inspection three times).
